title: Doctor Who Psychology by Travis Langley (.epub)
description:
Doctor Who Psychology: A Madman with a Box by Travis Langley (Editor)

Requirements: .ePUB reader

Overview: How does an immortal deal with death? What kind of person makes the best Companion? Why does the Doctor say he and Freud "got on very well"? How do the Daleks and Cybermen reflect concerns about losing our humanity? And what can looking at an ancient Time Lord teach us about real human nature? Doctor Who Psychology: A Madman with a Box explores these questions and many more. 

Genre: Non-Fiction > General
